{
  "stem": "19895.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we understood that what we are there for, again, was forced labor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were starting to dig trenches as well as tank trenches again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were given some very basic minimal food daily.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was much more organized because there was daily food for a while-- for a while.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and we were sleeping on hay.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was under cover.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the first week with hard labor, or the first two weeks with hard labor, went by.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then new transports arrived, which were forced labor units from the Russian border with an order-- well, our group, we were Tomas Stern and a couple of other names-- a name comes to my mind, his name was [?",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[RUSSIAN] ?] from the same building.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That few youngsters, we kind of try to keep together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because most of the people were not my age-- older.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we were the new arrivals, this forced labor units who came from the Russian front.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were arriving there in-- in large numbers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So our camp grew from some 2,000 people to probably 6,000 people in that location.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when they arrived, they were-- they were bringing something with them which I had no idea that exists.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That something was lice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Lice.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And lice is deadly. 'Cause lice on they clothes, which they wear for a year in this military, paramilitary units on the Russian fronts, they were lice-infected and that lice was the hotbed of typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were all trying to be-- and they told us, try to be clean, not to get lice, because lice can cause typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And what happened is that in the barrack, myself, which I was in, in a week or two, some people got tremendous fever.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They got ill.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
